{
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "chat_1",
      "provider": "chat",
      "config": {
        "hideForm": true,
        "mode": "Source",
        "parameters": {},
        "type": "chat"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 20,
          "y": 200
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_rocketride_1",
      "provider": "agent_rocketride",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "You are the Groundtruth research agent. You answer questions about research papers, their claims, methods, datasets, and — crucially — the executable evidence attached to them.",
          "The Neo4j knowledge graph contains: Paper, Author, Claim, Method, Dataset, Task, Run, Artifact nodes. Relationships: (Author)-[:WROTE]->(Paper), (Paper)-[:CITES]->(Paper), (Claim)-[:FROM]->(Paper), (Method)-[:DESCRIBED_IN]->(Paper), (Paper)-[:EVALUATED_ON]->(Dataset), (Paper)-[:ADDRESSES]->(Task), (Claim)-[:SUPPORTS|CONTRADICTS]->(Claim), (Run)-[:IMPLEMENTS]->(Method), (Run)-[:VALIDATES|REFUTES]->(Claim), (Run)-[:PRODUCED]->(Artifact).",
          "Use the Neo4j tool to query the graph before answering. Always cite claim ids (e.g. wilson2017-c2) and run ids in your answers.",
          "When asked about conflicts, query CONTRADICTS relationships between claims of different papers. When asked about evidence, query Run nodes and their VALIDATES/REFUTES links; distinguish claims with executable evidence from claims that are only asserted on paper.",
          "Keep answers concise and factual; this is a research evidence tool, not a chatbot.",
          "ACCURACY RULE: run metrics are stored as a JSON string on Run.metrics — quote numeric values EXACTLY as returned by the query (copy digit-for-digit, e.g. 0.425 not 0.05). If a value did not appear in a query result, say so instead of estimating."
        ],
        "max_waves": 6,
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "questions",
          "from": "chat_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 240,
          "y": 200
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 86
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_answers_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "config": {
        "laneName": "answers"
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "answers",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 460,
          "y": 200
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_openai_api_1",
      "provider": "llm_openai_api",
      "config": {
        "profile": "custom",
        "custom": {
          "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_GATEWAY_KEY}",
          "base_url": "${ROCKETRIDE_GATEWAY_BASE_URL}",
          "model": "${ROCKETRIDE_GATEWAY_MODEL}",
          "modelTotalTokens": 16384
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "llm",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        },
        {
          "classType": "llm",
          "from": "db_neo4j_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 60,
          "y": 380
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_internal_1",
      "provider": "memory_internal",
      "config": {
        "type": "memory_internal"
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "memory",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 280,
          "y": 380
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 66
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "db_neo4j_1",
      "provider": "db_neo4j",
      "config": {
        "profile": "default",
        "default": {
          "uri": "${ROCKETRIDE_NEO4J_URI}",
          "auth_method": "userpass",
          "user": "${ROCKETRIDE_NEO4J_USER}",
          "password": "${ROCKETRIDE_NEO4J_PASSWORD}",
          "database": "neo4j",
          "db_description": "Research knowledge graph linking papers to executable evidence. Nodes: Paper(id,title,year,arxiv,topic), Author(name), Claim(id,text,metric), Method(id,name,description,runnable_hint), Dataset(id,name), Task(id,name), Run(id,backend,exit_code,duration_s,status,metrics), Artifact(id,kind,content). Edges: WROTE, CITES, FROM (claim to paper), DESCRIBED_IN (method to paper), EVALUATED_ON, ADDRESSES, SUPPORTS/CONTRADICTS (claim to claim), IMPLEMENTS (run to method), VALIDATES/REFUTES (run to claim), PRODUCED (run to artifact). NOTE: the instance also contains unrelated SceneStyle/Product/Creator nodes from another project — ignore them.",
          "allow_execute": false,
          "max_attempts": 5
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "tool",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 500,
          "y": 380
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 135
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "tool_python_1",
      "provider": "tool_python",
      "config": {
        "type": "tool_python",
        "timeout": 300
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "tool",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 720,
          "y": 380
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 40
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "project_id": "33ff4b4b-6045-4374-81f9-fc8712488455",
  "viewport": {
    "x": 0,
    "y": 0,
    "zoom": 1
  },
  "version": 1
}